  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "The images were captured from Tencent street view panoramas using high-resolution panoramic cameras in various cities in China.",
    "The dataset covers different lighting and weather conditions.",
    "The original panoramas have a resolution of 8192×2048, which is cropped into four parts, resulting in a final dataset size of 2048×2048.",
    "TT-100K dataset includes a comprehensive range of 221 different traffic sign classes, with annotations provided for 128 classes.The VIVA Traffic Light Detection Benchmark (VIVA) [81]comprises six classes of large traffic light data, each representing a different color: green, yellow, red, left green, left yellow, and left red.The images have a resolution of 1,280 × 960, with a total of 30,000 images.",
    "This dataset is unique in that it includes both daytime and nighttime traffic light images.The LARA Traffic Light Recognition Public Benchmark [82] is a dataset collected from in-vehicle cameras in a densely populated urban environment."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "TT-100K dataset includes a comprehensive range of 221 different traffic sign classes, with annotations provided for 128 classes.The VIVA Traffic Light Detection Benchmark (VIVA) [81]comprises six classes of large traffic light data, each representing a different color: green, yellow, red, left green, left yellow, and left red.The images have a resolution of 1,280 × 960, with a total of 30,000 images.",
    "This dataset is unique in that it includes both daytime and nighttime traffic light images.The LARA Traffic Light Recognition Public Benchmark [82] is a dataset collected from in-vehicle cameras in a densely populated urban environment."
